graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebooks - Workbench Images]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|base images| UBI9[UBI9 Python 3.12<br/>registry.access.redhat.com]
    Notebooks -->|GPU support| CUDA[CUDA Base Images<br/>quay.io/rhoai/cuda-*]
    Notebooks -->|GPU support| ROCm[ROCm Base Images<br/>quay.io/rhoai/rocm-*]
    Notebooks -->|notebook UI| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 4.4]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| PyTorch[PyTorch 2.x]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x]
    Notebooks -->|XAI toolkit| TrustyAI[TrustyAI]
    Notebooks -->|LLM toolkit| LLMCompressor[LLMCompressor]
    Notebooks -->|CLI tool| OpenShiftCLI[OpenShift Client oc]
    Notebooks -->|pkg manager| uv[uv 0.8.12]
    Notebooks -->|pkg manager| micropipenv[micropipenv 1.9.0]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller] -->|launches pods| Notebooks
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|lists images| Notebooks
    KFPipelines[Kubeflow Pipelines] -->|executes tasks| Notebooks
    ModelMesh[Model Mesh] -->|runtime init| Notebooks

    %% Integration Points
    Notebooks -->|referenced by| ImageStreams[OpenShift ImageStreams]
    ImageStreams -->|pulls from| QuayIO[Quay.io Registry]
    Notebooks -->|data access| S3[S3 Storage]

    %% Build Infrastructure
    Konflux[Konflux Build System] -->|builds| Notebooks
    Konflux -->|pushes to| QuayIO
    Konflux -->|pulls base from| RedHatRegistry[registry.redhat.io]
    Konflux -->|source from| GitHub[GitHub Repository]
    Konflux -->|packages from| PyPI[pypi.org]

    %% Platform Integration
    OpenShiftRouter[OpenShift Router] -->|routes to| NotebookController
    OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar] -->|authenticates| OpenShiftRouter
    OAuthProxy -->|forwards to| Notebooks

